window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Mace and his allies set off on numerous perilous adventures to discover the location of the legendary Five Sisters.</b></p> <p>Their journeys lead them into the heart of the Spitrotz, the home of the black dragons, and high to the craggy peaks where the ice goddess dwells. With his allies finally gathered and the army assembled, Mace is ready to face the demon lord Altirax once and for all.</p> <p>But not all is as it appears. Someone has been tampering with the coding of the game since Mace first joined and the final battle will finally reveal the culprit and their intention.</p> <p><i>The Herald</i> is the exciting conclusion to the Immersion Online tetralogy. Old friends return, new enemies are revealed, and the war against Altirax will decide the fate of the Starborn and the entire Great Realm.</p>"; 
